{"type": "article", "id": 3931, "title": "W132系列灯饰", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-28T07:55:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233138uYPFnmSZEt4gCMws.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t熟悉瑞典照明品牌 Wastberg 的人都知道，他们的灯具素来以极简造型闻名，于是 Wastberg 邀请了擅长这一风格的日本设计工作室 Nendo ,为品牌带来 W132 系列的一组灯饰，分为圆锥体、球体及圆柱体的模块，几何搭配流线型的外形，塑造出来了诗意般的美感。相同的部件更可作为台灯、吊灯或者落地灯重复使用，只需配置加长支架或是加上吊线即可，灯罩还可以颠倒作为一个小的个人物品的存储容器。目前在中国，Wastberg 品牌的灯具仅在<a href=\"http://www.thedesignrepublic.com/brand_c.php?tid=82\" target=\"_blank\">上海设计共和余庆路店</a>有售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233135qAOkc15QlnbyRoLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233136eIdUmbWZJlDCkGvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233136kDH1iB2IN5eU8gw4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233137SZxATgzjaEmwR6IH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331378XumW3UtIKJ9Efvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233137oHRXP052pqJMK6h1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}